<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="618" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="20.[1434,2642,2650,3314]" pageId="20" pageNumber="618">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1434,1671,3123,3157]" pageId="20" pageNumber="618">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Phillips’s Gerbil is probably nocturnal and terrestrial, and digs burrOWS.
</paragraph>
